properties.propertyVal:
select
SRC_sf_account_program.*
from
$DO_GHL1_MY_BIOIQ_MD_SF_ACCOUNT_PROGRAM SRC_sf_account_program  join
(
	select program_code,max(pid) as pid
	from $DO_GHL1_MY_BIOIQ_MD_SF_ACCOUNT_PROGRAM b
	group by program_code
)b
on SRC_sf_account_program.program_code=b.program_code and SRC_sf_account_program.pid=b.pid

dCmd_Inst.dCmd:
UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'SUCCEEDED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,

SRC_source_count =  $RST_DF_UPDATE_dim_campaign_CLASSIFICATION.SRC_sf_account_program.SourceCount   , 
SRC_process_count =  $RST_DF_UPDATE_dim_campaign_CLASSIFICATION.SRC_sf_account_program.ProcessCount  , 
SRC_target_count =  $RST_DF_UPDATE_dim_campaign_CLASSIFICATION.SRC_sf_account_program.TargetCount  , 
SRC_bad_count =  $RST_DF_UPDATE_dim_campaign_CLASSIFICATION.SRC_sf_account_program.BadCount  ,
TGT_source_count =  $RST_DF_UPDATE_dim_campaign_CLASSIFICATION.TGT_dim_campaign.SourceCount   , 
TGT_process_count =  $RST_DF_UPDATE_dim_campaign_CLASSIFICATION.TGT_dim_campaign.ProcessCount  , 
TGT_target_count  =  $RST_DF_UPDATE_dim_campaign_CLASSIFICATION.TGT_dim_campaign.TargetCount   , 
TGT_bad_count =  $RST_DF_UPDATE_dim_campaign_CLASSIFICATION.TGT_dim_campaign.BadCount   ,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'JF_UPDATE_Program_Classification_SF' AND status= 'RUNNING'

UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'FAILED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'JF_UPDATE_Program_Classification_SF' AND status= 'RUNNING'

INSERT INTO control_load_history (data_flow_name, status, start_timestamp, created_at)
VALUES ('JF_UPDATE_Program_Classification_SF', 'RUNNING', $$CurrentTimeStamp, $$CurrentTimeStamp);

UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'ABORTED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'JF_UPDATE_Program_Classification_SF' AND status= 'RUNNING';
